author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the final big update it seems to GTA 5, a game I've been playing for 12 years. Finally we can retire and move on to the next year when the biggest game in the world will finally drop. Thanks for watching!

title: Finally Able To Retire..
